1
00:00:00,173 --> 00:00:01,780
Well, I don't know what I'll do.

2
00:00:04,520 --> 00:00:06,260
Please keep your eyes on the road,
dear.

3
00:00:07,600 --> 00:00:08,600
Mother...

4
00:00:09,460 --> 00:00:11,040
Okay, so here's the part.

5
00:00:11,239 --> 00:00:13,607
You're a secret agent,
and you've just stolen

6
00:00:13,608 --> 00:00:15,520
a super-advanced spy
car from the enemy.

7
00:00:15,720 --> 00:00:19,440
And now you have to parallel park it right
there.

8
00:00:20,580 --> 00:00:23,660
Now that is the stupidest plotline I have
ever heard.

9
00:00:23,840 --> 00:00:24,840
What do you mean?

10
00:00:25,220 --> 00:00:26,120
What do I mean?

11
00:00:26,121 --> 00:00:28,440
What's my motivation, Doug?

12
00:00:28,660 --> 00:00:29,660
What am I thinking?

13
00:00:29,720 --> 00:00:31,340
What does this mission mean to me?

